room_title: Escape room "CSI" by Optimal Escape in Evansville
room_description: You and your partner have been investigating a case regarding drug mafia business. Your partner has disappeared, but before disappearing he sent you an email saying that he had found some very crucial evidence. You and your team have gone to his office to search for the evidence. You have one hour to find the evidence and escape before you too disappear, for good!
